{"word":"G3805 - παθητός - pathētós - path-ay-tos' - Suffer","slug":"G3805","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παθητός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pathētós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>path-ay-tos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Suffer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>παθητός</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Pathetos</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>path-ay-tos'</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> passible, endued with the capacity of suffering, capable of feeling </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> subject to the necessity of suffering, destined to suffer </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from the same as <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 20:24,8 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Adjective <p />- Strong's: From the same as <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a>; <i>liable</i> (that is <i>doomed</i>) <i>to</i> experience <b><i>pain</i></b>: - suffer. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>"}]}